overview.overview: This product integrates TensorFlow, which is an end-to-end open source platform for machine learning. It has a comprehensive, flexible ecosystem of tools, libraries and community resources that lets researchers push the state-of-the-art in ML and developers easily build and deploy ML powered applications.

highlights: TensorBoard installed, running state through the graphical management program

childMarkdownRemark.html: TensorFlow is an end-to-end open source machine learning platform. It has a comprehensive and flexible ecosystem, which contains a variety of tools, libraries and community resources. In terms of machine learning, it can easily build models, carry out reliable machine learning production anytime and anywhere, and conduct powerful research experiments.

faq.key: What are the requirements for TensorFlow to implement GPU support?
faq.value: Requires NVIDIA® GPU graphics card along with drivers and tools. For details, please refer to : https://www.tensorflow.org/install/gpu
